{"tid":1438300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不樂觀，求計仔和大量文宣，各位同我每日死去集會！","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:51:40.000Z","uid":261649,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3cd61fac307ac8b17e60d0bc0e17a327271258","tid":1438300,"uid":261649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"感覺到連登外既香港人開始無左衝勁<br />\n香港人好易對事情麻木<br />\n再係咁落去只會越黎越少人集會<br />\n前線又越黎越多比黑警拉<br />\n希望各位連登仔女幫手做文宣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煲大警黑合作、黑警暴力濫權</span></span><br />\n得閒去印傳單派、等車都可以airdrop人<br />\n大家各有各做，勿忘初心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好忘記每一個比黑警拉既義士<br />\n唔好忘記黑警開既每一槍、每一個催淚彈！</span></span><br />\n大家想要傳單同印刷地方PM我<br />\n<br />\n同堆各位同我每日死去集會！<br />\n少左你就少一分力<br />\n其他人就有更大機會被捕<br />\n大家要記得當日200萬人上街既初衷"},{"pid":"5febb4d26d1a5fb6890ab7645ee60d897e1f20d3","tid":1438300,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:33:27.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cc1dd2109c0c41224b18af87fd2ddebdd85b77","tid":1438300,"uid":261649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"3f7986a046da5b19789db6093c96ae6cc497f590","tid":1438300,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:55:03.000Z","msg":"【811港島東大遊行】 10號下晝4點半將進行上訴聆訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438318/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438318/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【811港島東大遊行】當日維園會照有集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438329/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438329/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrmcoLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrmcoLA.jpg&h=b4db3112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港島東集會<br />\n日期：2019年8月11日(星期日)<br />\n時間：下午1時正<br />\n地點：維多利亞公園4至6號足球場<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情有待通知<br />\n<br />\n集會以和平理性方式進行，要求政府正面回應五大訴求，唯警方選擇以種種理由拒絕遊行申請，無疑令人有感政府嘗試打壓市民的遊行權利和自由，因此我們呼籲市民更加要站出來，繼續遍地開花，堅守五大訴求。"},{"pid":"4fd16d5c21a87067df13a8a8ff82b60dec4d5d33","tid":1438300,"uid":261649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"大家聽日同我死出黎發夢集會！"},{"pid":"0dc5159c2afdd25e92a880c17543804463fc2186","tid":1438300,"uid":261649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"大家聽日同我死去發夢集會！"},{"pid":"305ba87d03f8be1b6b4e2787d0beaeae55590f26","tid":1438300,"uid":261649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"dd4869613a3a0349c9024fbc6e1c5f363448605c","tid":1438300,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}